last_episode_to_air.name: Episode 8
last_episode_to_air.overview: Desperate to banish visions of the night at Clive's house, Alyssa suddenly disappears, sending James into a panic.

name: The End of the F***ing World
original_name: The End of the F***ing World
overview: James is 17 and is pretty sure he is a psychopath. Alyssa, also 17, is the cool and moody new girl at school. The pair make a connection and she persuades him to embark on a darkly comedic road trip in search of her real father.

seasons.name: Season 1
seasons.overview: A budding teen psychopath and a rebel hungry for adventure embark on a star-crossed road trip in this darkly comic series based on a graphic novel.

seasons.name: Season 2
seasons.overview: Two years later, Alyssa dives headfirst into a new life – just as a woman with a grudge sets out on a murderous quest for revenge.

tagline: Some love stories begin at the end.

episodes.name: Episode 1
episodes.overview: Bored with killing animals, 17-year-old James is busy plotting his first real murder when brash new girl Alyssa catches him off guard at school.

episodes.name: Episode 2
episodes.overview: On the road, James and Alyssa quickly realize they're in over their heads, but neither wants to admit it. A friendly army vet offers them help.

episodes.name: Episode 3
episodes.overview: Hoping to lie low for a few days, the pair breaks into a home stocked with swanky amenities -- and a disturbing secret.

episodes.name: Episode 4
episodes.overview: Alyssa begins to see James in a new light as they scramble to cover their tracks and alter their appearance after a harrowing night.

episodes.name: Episode 5
episodes.overview: A flashback to a painful moment from childhood prompts James to change his plans. Out of cash, Alyssa resorts to shoplifting.

episodes.name: Episode 6
episodes.overview: James reveals he's a man of hidden talents, Alyssa squares off with a shrewd gas station manager, and Eunice makes a startling discovery.

episodes.name: Episode 7
episodes.overview: As Alyssa reconnects with her dad, a worried James faces a dilemma. Eunice and Teri clash over the best way to approach the teens.

episodes.name: Episode 8
episodes.overview: Eunice goes rogue, Leslie shows his true colors, and Alyssa and James plan their escape -- but soon realize they're out of time.

episodes.name: Episode 1
episodes.overview: Newly released from prison, a brooding young woman named Bonnie sets out to avenge the death of her lover.

episodes.name: Episode 2
episodes.overview: Just as Alyssa claws her way back to a semblance of a normal life, she discovers her past isn't done with her yet.

episodes.name: Episode 3
episodes.overview: After an awkward encounter at the café, Alyssa wakes up on her big day with nagging doubts about what she wants from life.

episodes.name: Episode 4
episodes.overview: A flat tire forces the unlikely trio of travelers to seek refuge at a roadside inn run by a man who's desperate for company.

episodes.name: Episode 5
episodes.overview: While Bonnie scrambles to cover her tracks and tend to her injury, James tries to figure out where things stand with Alyssa.

episodes.name: Episode 6
episodes.overview: Alyssa decides it's time to set things right at home, James searches for a new plan, and Bonnie resumes her quest with fresh vigor.

episodes.name: Episode 7
episodes.overview: After discovering Bonnie's true intentions, James races to help Alyssa, and a tense showdown unfolds inside the café.

episodes.name: Episode 8
episodes.overview: Desperate to banish visions of the night at Clive's house, Alyssa suddenly disappears, sending James into a panic.
